text: And one more makes exactly ten.
— Toby to Quinn after punching wood to make ladders.

texts.text: Toby is a character in the Minecraft Mini-Series and part of Team Stone Beach with Quinn. He helps her in trying to escape CommuniKate's game show and then Poseidon's game show after he takes over in the Greek Isles.
Toby has neat brown hair, green eyes, glasses, and dark-tan skin. He wears a light blue button up shirt, slate colored pants, and dark dray shoes.
Toby is helpful, analytical, and methodical. He is kind-hearted towards his friends and nervous towards opposition.

Toby is shown to be a stone beach miner when "interviewed" in between clips.
He is similar to Radar in many aspects.
